task.summary: Now supports holding buttons and simultaneous button presses
Now uses async task instead of spawning explicate thread
Preferences implemented, app uses saved ip and port, places user in settings if settigns not set
Removed dependency on Datagram, moved functionality inside app. Now have toggleable button to turn controller on and off. Successfully communicates with arduino

This adds the functions at the request of the Scotland engineering team. We have modified the strings being sent for each command. They are as follows : String......Command ============= d......drive forward b......backwards p......park/stop/neutral (needs work) f.......realign front wheels l ......left r.......right
The power button has also been configured to send a hello message to authenticate with the server.
